fulltitle: Camay Murphy speaks on her father Cab Calloway.

description: Just after being told the location of her father's childhood home, Camay Murphy sat down for this interview to talk about her memories, opinions, thoughts, and ideas for the location.  She also speaks extensively about his unique relationship with the Jewish community which lasted for his entire career.
